  "title": "Reliability-First Queue Risk for GPU Clusters: Calibration, SLOs, and Reproducible Operational Integration",
  "description": "Reproducible scientific-software artifact accompanying the ISS26 paper. Includes the full calibration-aware pipeline (feature engineering, five model families, isotonic post-hoc calibration, tier qualification, PSI drift detection, sliding-window recalibration), sample data for four cluster environments (EKS, Slurm+DCGM, Alibaba, Google Borg), trained calibrators, all benchmark results, and a single Jupyter notebook that regenerates every figure in the paper.",
